0xED0935B5.name: ADD_MINIMAP_OVERLAY_WITH_DEPTH

params.name: name
params.description: The path to a `.gfx` file in the current resource. It has to be specified as a `file`.

params.name: depth
params.description: The depth of new overlay on the minimap. Pass `-1` for game to figure out the highest depth itself. Should not be greater than `0x7EFFFFFD`.

0xED0935B5.description: Loads a minimap overlay from a GFx file in the current resource.
